{
  "stem": "12402.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Bruno, come here, and tells me, come over, and he gives me-- a basket of bread was 25 in a basket, you know, like a straw basket-- we used to load up 25 bread each basket, and load up every morning.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So, he tells me, take a basket of bread and cut the bread in three, you know, and told me to cut in another basket.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And lined up, there must have been 20 girls standing there. 20 girls came, and I don't know how they got out of there-- they would watch them with the-- with the machine guns and every thing.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They could have sneaked out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They're a lot of-- and said, line them up, you in charge, give everybody.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That was-- I couldn't forget it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean, he was-- he was a good man.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So what happened, so I give every girl a portion.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The one girl that said to him, lieber Herr, in Jewish-- in-- in-- in broken German, lieber Herr, can-- can I have another portion?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Like in German, and said.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He looks at me, and see, this is a Jude, this is a Jew.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Give 'em a finger, he wants two.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that's a joke, I remember this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I can't forget it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So the girls left, and I made up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I asked the girls-- I asked them, where are they taking you?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Know where they're going to them?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They don't know where.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I waited, and they went, probably they're gonna take us, but the minute we get back, they're going to chase us again.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Anyway, I waited and waited, and I load up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I stretched it out as this much as I can, maybe-- they had to go by the bakery.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Maybe I'll recognize something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Maybe I'll see something.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
